OL,3,CDavie speech and annual plan light on
OL,4,Cdetail about future cuts
OL,6,GThe speculation was intense. The BBC
OL,7,GDirector-General's speech on Tuesday
OL,8,Gwas, the headlines said, set to
OL,9,Gannounce some of the biggest changes
OL,10,Gin the corporation's history.
OL,12,FMeanwhile the corporation's annual
OL,13,Fplan, published later in the week, was
OL,14,Fpresumed to be set to reveal the fate
OL,15,Fof some significant programmes and
OL,16,Fservices.
OL,18,FThere was, at least in retrospect,
OL,19,Fmore than a bit of hyperbole by some
OL,20,Fcommentators.
