OL,6,FTim Davie's speech was genuinely
OL,7,Fsignificant and set out a blueprint
OL,8,Ffor the way forward.
OL,10,FThere are important questions about
OL,11,Fthe BBC's future role. News coverage
OL,12,Ffocused on the question of the future
OL,13,Fof the TV licence.
OL,15,FIt is certainly interesting that the
OL,16,Fcorporation is not wedded to the
OL,17,Flicence in its traditional form and is
OL,18,Fopen to the possibility of reform.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/6
