OL,3,CDavie speech and annual plan light on
OL,4,Cdetail about future cuts
OL,6,FMr Davie did highlight some tough
OL,7,Fchoices to decommission programmes in
OL,8,Frecent months.
OL,10,FTo be fair though, most of the
OL,11,Fprogrammes he mentioned had probably
OL,12,Fcome to the end of their natural runs.
OL,13,FBut pressure on budgets means less
OL,14,Foverall is being made so axed
OL,15,Fprogrammes may not be directly
OL,16,Freplaced.
OL,18,FThen on Thursday, came the annual plan.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/6
