OL,3,CDavie speech and annual plan light on
OL,4,Cdetail about future cuts
OL,6,FIn the detail, again, were some
OL,7,Fpotentially controversial decisions to
OL,8,Freduce the hours of certain kinds of
OL,9,Fnew programmes.
OL,11,FBut it was just as significant there
OL,12,Fwas no word of any potentially
OL,13,Fcontroversial decisions to axe any
OL,14,Fpopular programmes.
OL,16,FThere has been much speculation
OL,17,Frecently over the future of Casualty.
OL,18,FIt wasn't even mentioned.
OL,20,FAnd it would appear BBC Four and CBBC
OL,21,Fas linear channels are safe for
OL,22,Fanother year.
