OL,6,FNo doubt more genuinely difficult
OL,7,Fdecisions are coming.
OL,9,FIn the case of Casualty, will the
OL,10,Fnumber of episodes be cut further or
OL,11,Fcould it ` despite denials ` be coming
OL,12,Ftowards, hopefully, a dignified end?
OL,14,FWe will see in the fullness of time.
OL,16,FBut it is, again, a reminder not to be
OL,17,Fcarried away by speculation or see
OL,18,Fcertain changes as inevitable.
